# Comprehensive PILOT Language Test
# Tests all major PILOT commands and features

# Text output
T:Welcome to PILOT Language Test Suite
T:This test exercises all PILOT commands

# Input and variables
T:Testing Input and Variables
A:NAME
T:Hello *NAME*!
U:AGE=25
T:Your age is set to *AGE*

# Arithmetic
T:Testing Arithmetic
C:RESULT = 10 + 5
T:10 + 5 = *RESULT*
C:RESULT = AGE * 2
T:Double your age: *RESULT*

# Labels and jumps
L:START_LOOP
T:In the loop
U:COUNTER=COUNTER+1
J(COUNTER<3):START_LOOP

# Match conditions
T:Testing match conditions
M:YES=Y
T:You answered YES
M:NO=N  
T:You answered NO

# Conditional branching
T:Testing Y: and N: conditions
A:ANSWER
Y:*ANSWER*=YES
T:Positive response detected
N:*ANSWER*=NO
T:Negative response detected

# Match and text
MT:Enter a number
A:NUMBER
M:*NUMBER*=5
T:You entered exactly 5!

# More complex expressions
C:FIBONACCI1=1
C:FIBONACCI2=1
C:FIBONACCI3=FIBONACCI1+FIBONACCI2
T:Fibonacci sequence: *FIBONACCI1*, *FIBONACCI2*, *FIBONACCI3*

# Testing string operations
U:GREETING=Hello World
T:Greeting: *GREETING*

# Final output
T:All PILOT commands tested successfully!
END